title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Return to Oz
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Return to Oz
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe venture into the magical world of Oz – not the 1939 version, but the dark fantasy stylings of 1985’s “Return to Oz,” featuring electrotherapy, nightmarish wheelers and other strange delights.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
